<span style="color: #608b4e;"># Database Selection Guide</span>

<span style="color: #4ec9b0;">PostgreSQL:</span> Transactional data, ACID compliance
  - User accounts, orders, payments
  - Relational data with complex queries

<span style="color: #4ec9b0;">MongoDB:</span> Document storage, flexible schema
  - Product catalogs, user profiles
  - Semi-structured, rapidly changing data

<span style="color: #4ec9b0;">Redis:</span> High-speed cache, ephemeral data
  - Session storage, API rate limiting
  - Real-time leaderboards, pub/sub

<span style="color: #4ec9b0;">Elasticsearch:</span> Full-text search, log analytics
  - Product search, autocomplete
  - Application logs, metrics
                </div>
